title: Minnal Murali
subTitle: Jaison, a young tailor, gains superpowers after being struck by lightning. However, he must thwart the evil intentions of an unexpected adversary to become the superhero that his rural village needs.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: Vijay, a dedicated police officer, is shattered to discover his brother Aftab is a ruthless criminal. Torn between duty and love, Vijay embarks on a relentless quest to bring him to justice.

title: Time Machine
subTitle: When Elango and Pulivetti find a time machine, they decide to use it for their benefit. While meddling with time, they prevent a gangster's death and this lands them in trouble.

title: Time Machine
subTitle: A young boy invents world's first time machine but still cannot keep his loved ones safe from fate's inevitability, rendering him helpless despite the extraordinary power at his command.

title: Dhruva
subTitle: A committed police officer, Dhruva, uncovers a web of organised crime headed by a scientist, Siddharth Abhimanyu. But when Dhruva tries to build a case against him, he faces many challenges.

title: Agent Chanakya
subTitle: Arjun, a highly sought-after RAW agent, is known for his skills at catching some of the most hardened criminals. However, he falls in danger when he goes after Ibrahim Qureshi, a terrorist.

title: Rider
subTitle: As love blossoms between orphans Chinnu and Kitty, fate separates them as children. However, they grow up yearning to find each other.

title: Vijay Raghavan
subTitle: An honest IAS officer devotes his life to the upliftment of the youth in his locality. However, a corrupt businessman's ploy to poison these young minds compels him to challenge the criminal.

title: Sita Ram
subTitle: Ram, a young boy, lives in a monastery waiting for Sita to return and take care of him. However, Sita returns, years later, but with an ulterior motive.

title: Dangerous Khiladi 2
subTitle: A corrupt minister's daughter finds a diary containing details about a couple's relationship. When the story ends abruptly, she sets out to find the person who wrote it.

title: Veeram The Powerman
subTitle: A fearless young man vows to mend his violent ways after falling in love with a beautiful maiden. However, he is forced to resort to violence after a gang of nefarious criminals pursue his lady love.

title: Veeram The Powerman
subTitle: A fearless young man vows to mend his violent ways after falling in love with a beautiful maiden. However, he is forced to resort to violence after a gang of nefarious criminals pursue his lady love.

title: Kartoos
subTitle: ACP Jay Suryavanshi assigns an inmate on death row, Jeet, the task of killing Jagat, a terrorist. Things take a turn when Jeet falls in love with Mini and gets distracted from his mission.

title: Mohini
subTitle: Vaishnavi and Sandeep, a couple in love, are engaged to be married. However, things spiral out of control when she gets possessed by a lookalike who is thirsty for vengeance.

title: The Return of Abhimanyu
subTitle: A military officer borrows money from a bank using fake papers for his sister's marriage. However, when the money goes missing from his account, he begins an investigation that leads him to a hacker.

title: International Khiladi: The Iron Man
subTitle: Amrita's parents get killed. Years later, she falls in love with Aditya only to learn that he was the one who was accused of her parents' murder.

title: Meri Taqat Mera Faisla
subTitle: A young man follows in his father's footsteps by working for the welfare of the people living in his district. However, a corrupt politician threatens to thwart his plans.

title: Power Unlimited
subTitle: The home minister asks Tirupathi to impersonate the deceased ACP Baldev, his lookalike, to catch Ganguly, a dreaded gangster. After taking over his new role, he finds many startling revelations.

title: Double Attack
subTitle: Siddharth and Charan, two lookalikes who are fighting their own battles against evildoers, cross paths and join forces to take down Rawat, a ruthless minister.

title: Kabzaa - The Mafia Raaj
subTitle: Vijay Chandra, a determined police aspirant, battles a local MLA's corrupt efforts to seize his family's land. Joined by other wronged citizens, he takes a stand for justice and honor.

title: Indrani: Epic-1 Dharam vs Karam
subTitle: When China threatens to destroy India in the future, the Indian Super Force (ISF) sends agent Indrani back to the past to find a solution.

title: Indrani: Epic-1 Dharam vs Karam
subTitle: When China threatens to destroy India in the future, the Indian Super Force (ISF) sends agent Indrani back to the past to find a solution.

title: Athiratha
subTitle: Following a family legacy, a youngster ventures into journalism and investigates a scandal involving a powerful politician. However, his life moves downhill after he is arrested under a false charge.

title: Vishnu Shastra
subTitle: For the protagonist 'abbai' (Sree Vishnu), life is all about taking care of his elder sister and doting parents until they are all killed in a mysterious bomb blast. The plot follows this youngster going all out to avenge their deaths.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi 2
subTitle: Balu grows up without the love of a family due to his parents' untimely death. Later, he decides to establish a firm to help people like himself receive the affection they missed out on.

title: Harom Hara (The Revolt)
subTitle: Subrahmanyam loses his job and faces financial ruin. In an attempt to overcome his limitations, he gets involved in the illegal arms trade, eventually becoming one of South India's notorious arms dealers.

title: Golmaal 3
subTitle: Cupid strikes when Pritam, a single father, comes across his college sweetheart, Geeta, in Goa. However, when their respective children go at war with each other, the two find it difficult to reunite.

title: Gatta Kusthi
subTitle: Veera has a preconceived set of criteria for what he wants in a bride. However, he ends up unexpectedly marrying a woman who is the complete opposite of his expectations.

title: Saindhav
subTitle: A man with a traumatic past is compelled to encounter an crime boss so that he can rescue his daughter from a health problem.

title: DD Returns
subTitle: An event manager and his friends hide the money they stole in a haunted bungalow to evade the police but when they go back to retrieve it, the ghosts force them to play a dangerous game.
